</p>

</div>
<div id="fn" class="footnote"><a class="note-ref" href="#PJA11d079n1-ptr" id="PJA11d079n1">1</a>

   <p>Let no day pass without something done.</p>

</div>
<div class="footnote"><a class="note-ref" href="#PJA11d079n2-ptr" id="PJA11d079n2">2</a>

   <p>See <abbr title="fade=[ on ] fadespeed=[0.1] windowlock=[on] cssbody=[ boxover ] header=[]  body=[ John Adams (17351826) ]">JA</abbr>s Diary entry for <a href="default.xqy?keys=ADMS-print-01-02-02-0009-0008-0008" class="document">15 Dec. 1779</a> (<span class="ref-st" title="fade=[ on ] fadespeed=[0.1] windowlock=[on] cssbody=[ boxover ] header=[]  body=[ &lt;i&gt;Diary and Autobiography of John Adams&lt;/i&gt;, ed. L. H. Butterfield and others, Cambridge, 1961; 4 vols. ]"><span class="hi-italic" style="font-style: italic;">Diary and Autobiography</span></span>, 2:409).</p>

